{
  "stem": "2966.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was a little hole in the ground where you used to use for refrigeration in the summer, and in the winter.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because in the winter it kept things warm, and the summer kept things cool.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Anyway, I started enlarging that thing under the floor, and I built a hole of maybe-- I don't know, maybe six by 10, and maybe four feet high.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You could not stand up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was hidden there for a few months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "At the same time, I went back to see my father, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I asked him to come back, to be hidden with me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] At that unfortunate time, also, they uncovered the hiding place where my sister was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But it so happened that that day, when they uncovered them and they took them all to be shot, she was not there that day.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She went to that place where all the people were working.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That was called [POLISH], [GERMAN] in German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In Polish was [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Let's call it a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Let's call it this way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "She was there for that day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I took my father and my sister with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But because we had no money-- we had very little-- and the people were very poor that were hiding us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They really couldn't feed us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So whatever we had, we used to sell-- a extra pair of pants, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I don't remember what we had already-- we sold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And there came to a point where we had nothing else to sell.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So my father and my sister voluntarily went to that camp, because there was no way to survive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "There was no place to hide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "A lot of people were hiding in the forests.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
